--*
--* IS A: PARTIAL_SET(K,T) BOUNDED_PARTIAL_MULTISET(K,T1,T)
--*
--* REQUIRED CLASSES: BOUNDED_SET(T) PARTIAL_SET(K,T1,T) EXCEPTION__BOUNDED_MULTISET_INS\
--* EXCEPTION__BOUNDED_MULTISET_UNION EXCEPTION__MULTISET EXCEPTION__SET_ADD \
--* EXCEPTION__SET_DISJOINT_UNION EXCEPTION__PARTIAL_MULTISET_LOOKUP
--*
--* EXCEPTIONS: EXCEPTION__BOUNDED_MULTISET_INS EXCEPTION__BOUNDED_MULTISET_UNION \
--* EXCEPTION__MULTISET EXCEPTION__SET_ADD EXCEPTION__SET_DISJOINT_UNION \
--* EXCEPTION__PARTIAL_MULTISET_LOOKUP
